query: SELECT p.id, p.leadId, p.addressLine1, COUNT(c.id) as contact_count FROM properties p LEFT JOIN contacts c ON c.propertyId = p.id WHERE p.dealMachinePropertyId IS NOT NULL GROUP BY p.id HAVING contact_count > 3 ORDER BY contact_count DESC LIMIT 5;
